text: Sir George Denys, 1st Baronet (1788–1857), of Blacklands House, Chelsea, Middlesex, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Kingston upon Hull 1812 to 1818. ==Arms== ==References== Category:1788 births Category:1857 deaths Category:Baronets in the Baronetage of England Category:People from Chelsea, London Category:Politicians from Yorkshire Category:Members of the Parliament of the United Kingdom for English constituencies Category:UK MPs 1812–1818
